<dl id="n12128j"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n12" href="#n12128j">N12 (VI.B.14)</a>:  <a href="../../FF/fnbs/n12all.htm#n12128j"> 128(j)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> archery v cavalry / guns v bows</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">Un grand malaise p&egrave;se sur cette soci&eacute;t&eacute; m&eacute;di&eacute;vale finissante. La pompeuse chevalerie devient inutile maintenant que les archers &agrave; pied font meilleure besogne de guerre que les cavalcades. <br><font color="green">[A great illness weighed on this dying medieval society. The pompous cavalry had become useless now that archers on foot were much more useful in a war than horses.]</font> <small> Matthieu-Maxime Gorce, <a name="STVF" href="../../FF/fdra/fdex.htm#STVF"><cite title="source">Saint Vincent Ferrier</cite></a> (1924) 63</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
